  "detailed_description": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Holidays Survivors</strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Step into a festive battle for survival in <i>Holidays Survivors</i>! Choose your hero—Santa, the determined bringer of joy; his trusty, swift Deer companion; or the resourceful, quick-thinking Elf—and defend the holiday season from a grotesque outbreak.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3244190/extras/50d9ae9247c62dd93735b0b9ee32c7f6.avif?t=1735240278\" width=616 height=352 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >The infected have mutated into horrifying half-insect creatures, and unholy demons lurk in the snow-covered landscapes. Armed with an arsenal weapons, you must overcome relentless waves of monstrous foes.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >🎅 The holidays have never been this deadly—or this fun! Can you save the season? 🎅</p>",
  "about_the_game": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Holidays Survivors</strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Step into a festive battle for survival in <i>Holidays Survivors</i>! Choose your hero—Santa, the determined bringer of joy; his trusty, swift Deer companion; or the resourceful, quick-thinking Elf—and defend the holiday season from a grotesque outbreak.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3244190/extras/50d9ae9247c62dd93735b0b9ee32c7f6.avif?t=1735240278\" width=616 height=352 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >The infected have mutated into horrifying half-insect creatures, and unholy demons lurk in the snow-covered landscapes. Armed with an arsenal weapons, you must overcome relentless waves of monstrous foes.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >🎅 The holidays have never been this deadly—or this fun! Can you save the season? 🎅</p>",
